{
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "verse_number": 1,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:1",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ",
      "translation": "1. Aku bersumpah dengan hari Kiamat,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "verse_number": 2,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:2",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلنَّفۡسِ ٱللَّوَّامَةِ",
      "translation": "2. Dan aku bersumpah demi jiwa yang selalu menyesali (dirinya sendiri).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "verse_number": 3,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:3",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَلَّن نَّجۡمَعَ عِظَامَهُۥ",
      "translation": "3. Apakah manusia mengira, bahwa Kami tidak akan mengumpulkan (kembali) tulang belulangnya?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "verse_number": 4,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:4",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "بَلَىٰ قَٰدِرِينَ عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّسَوِّيَ بَنَانَهُۥ",
      "translation": "4. (Bahkan) Kami mampu menyusun (kembali) jari jemarinya dengan sempurna.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "verse_number": 5,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:5",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "بَلۡ يُرِيدُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ لِيَفۡجُرَ أَمَامَهُۥ",
      "translation": "5. Tetapi manusia hendak membuat maksiat terus-menerus.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "verse_number": 6,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:6",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَسۡـَٔلُ أَيَّانَ يَوۡمُ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ",
      "translation": "6. Dia bertanya, “Kapankah hari Kiamat?”",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "verse_number": 7,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:7",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَإِذَا بَرِقَ ٱلۡبَصَرُ",
      "translation": "7. Maka apabila mata terbelalak (ketakutan),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "verse_number": 8,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:8",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَخَسَفَ ٱلۡقَمَرُ",
      "translation": "8. Dan bulan pun telah hilang cahayanya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "verse_number": 9,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:9",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَجُمِعَ ٱلشَّمۡسُ وَٱلۡقَمَرُ",
      "translation": "9. Lalu matahari dan bulan dikumpulkan,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "verse_number": 10,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:10",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَقُولُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذٍ أَيۡنَ ٱلۡمَفَرُّ",
      "translation": "10. Pada hari itu manusia berkata, “Ke mana tempat lari?”",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "verse_number": 11,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:11",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّا لَا وَزَرَ",
      "translation": "11. Tidak! Tidak ada tempat berlindung!",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "verse_number": 12,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:12",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمُسۡتَقَرُّ",
      "translation": "12. Hanya kepada Tuhanmu tempat kembali pada hari itu.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "verse_number": 13,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:13",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يُنَبَّؤُاْ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بِمَا قَدَّمَ وَأَخَّرَ",
      "translation": "13. Pada hari itu diberitakan kepada manusia apa yang telah dikerjakannya dan apa yang telah dilalaikannya.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "verse_number": 14,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:14",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "بَلِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ عَلَىٰ نَفۡسِهِۦ بَصِيرَةٞ",
      "translation": "14. Bahkan manusia menjadi saksi atas dirinya sendiri,*(880)",
      "footnotes": "*880). Anggota badan manusia menjadi saksi terhadap pekerjaan yang telah mereka lakukan seperti tersebut dalam Surah An-Nūr (24) ayat 24."
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "verse_number": 15,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:15",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَلَوۡ أَلۡقَىٰ مَعَاذِيرَهُۥ",
      "translation": "15. Dan meskipun dia mengemukakan alasan-alasannya.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "verse_number": 16,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:16",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لَا تُحَرِّكۡ بِهِۦ لِسَانَكَ لِتَعۡجَلَ بِهِۦٓ",
      "translation": "16. Jangan engkau (Muhammad) gerakkan lidahmu (untuk membaca Al-Qur`ān) karena hendak cepat-cepat (menguasai)nya.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "verse_number": 17,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:17",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا جَمۡعَهُۥ وَقُرۡءَانَهُۥ",
      "translation": "17. Sesungguhnya Kami yang akan mengumpulkannya (di dadamu) dan membacakannya.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "verse_number": 18,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:18",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَإِذَا قَرَأۡنَٰهُ فَٱتَّبِعۡ قُرۡءَانَهُۥ",
      "translation": "18. Apabila Kami telah selesai membacakannya, maka ikutilah bacaannya itu.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "verse_number": 19,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:19",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا بَيَانَهُۥ",
      "translation": "19. Kemudian sesungguhnya Kami yang akan menjelaskannya.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "verse_number": 20,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:20",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّا بَلۡ تُحِبُّونَ ٱلۡعَاجِلَةَ",
      "translation": "20. Tidak! Bahkan kamu mencintai kehidupan dunia,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "verse_number": 21,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:21",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَتَذَرُونَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةَ",
      "translation": "21. dan mengabaikan (kehidupan) akhirat.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "verse_number": 22,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:22",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاضِرَةٌ",
      "translation": "22. Wajah-wajah (orang mukmin) pada hari itu berseri-seri.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "verse_number": 23,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:23",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَىٰ رَبِّهَا نَاظِرَةٞ",
      "translation": "23. Memandang Tuhannya.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "verse_number": 24,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:24",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بَاسِرَةٞ",
      "translation": "24. Dan wajah-wajah (orang kafir) pada hari itu muram,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "verse_number": 25,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:25",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "تَظُنُّ أَن يُفۡعَلَ بِهَا فَاقِرَةٞ",
      "translation": "25. Mereka yakin bahwa akan ditimpakan kepadanya malapetaka yang sangat dahsyat.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "verse_number": 26,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:26",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّآ إِذَا بَلَغَتِ ٱلتَّرَاقِيَ",
      "translation": "26. Tidak! Apabila (nyawa) telah sampai ke kerongkongan,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "verse_number": 27,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:27",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَقِيلَ مَنۡۜ رَاقٖ",
      "translation": "27. Dan dikatakan (kepadanya), “Siapa yang dapat menyembuhkan?”",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "verse_number": 28,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:28",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَظَنَّ أَنَّهُ ٱلۡفِرَاقُ",
      "translation": "28. Dan dia yakin bahwa itulah waktu perpisahan (dengan dunia),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "verse_number": 29,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:29",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلۡتَفَّتِ ٱلسَّاقُ بِٱلسَّاقِ",
      "translation": "29. Dan bertaut betis (kiri) dengan betis (kanan),*(881)",
      "footnotes": "*881). Karena hebatnya penderitaan pada saat akan mati dan ketakutan akan meninggalkan dunia dan menghadapi akhirat."
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "verse_number": 30,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:30",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمَسَاقُ",
      "translation": "30. kepada Tuhanmulah pada hari itu kamu dihalau.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "verse_number": 31,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:31",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَلَا صَدَّقَ وَلَا صَلَّىٰ",
      "translation": "31. Karena dia (dahulu) tidak mau membenarkan (Al-Qur`ān dan Rasul) dan tidak mau melaksanakan salat,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "verse_number": 32,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:32",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَلَٰكِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ",
      "translation": "32. tetapi justru dia mendustakan (Rasul) dan berpaling (dari kebenaran),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "verse_number": 33,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:33",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ ذَهَبَ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ يَتَمَطَّىٰٓ",
      "translation": "33. kemudian dia pergi kepada keluarganya, dengan sombong.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "verse_number": 34,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:34",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰ",
      "translation": "34. Celakalah kamu! Maka celakalah!",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "verse_number": 35,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:35",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰٓ",
      "translation": "35. Sekali lagi, celakalah kamu (manusia)! Maka celakalah!",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "verse_number": 36,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:36",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَن يُتۡرَكَ سُدًى",
      "translation": "36. Apakah manusia mengira, dia akan dibiarkan begitu saja (tanpa pertanggungjawaban)?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "verse_number": 37,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:37",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَلَمۡ يَكُ نُطۡفَةٗ مِّن مَّنِيّٖ يُمۡنَىٰ",
      "translation": "37. Bukankah dia mulanya hanya setetes mani yang ditumpahkan (ke dalam rahim).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "verse_number": 38,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:38",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ كَانَ عَلَقَةٗ فَخَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ",
      "translation": "38. Kemudian (mani itu) menjadi sesuatu yang melekat, lalu Allah menciptakannya dan menyempurnakannya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "verse_number": 39,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:39",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَجَعَلَ مِنۡهُ ٱلزَّوۡجَيۡنِ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰٓ",
      "translation": "39. lalu Dia menjadikan darinya sepasang laki-laki dan perempuan.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
